{"cursor":"22562","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"\nAn 'action figure' is a posable character figurine, made of plastic or other\nmaterials, and often based upon characters from a film, comic book, video game,\nor television program. These action figures are usually marketed towards boys\nand adult collectors. It is argued that action figures are particularly popular\nwith boys because they represent traditional masculine traits and are closely\nassociated with the public sphere. While most commonly marketed as a\nchildren's toy, the action figure has gained wide acceptance as an adult\ncollector item. In such a case, the item may be produced and designed on the\nassumption it will be bought solely for display. Action figures are also known\nas action dolls.\n","linknr":284,"url":"Action_figure","recorded":1362371286,"links":30,"instances":["texture","2002","toy_line","comics","action_figures","masters_of_the_universe","comics"],"pdf":[],"categories":["Action figures","Dolls","Toys based on works","1964 introductions","Toy collecting"],"headings":["History","Production","Characteristics and features","See also","References"],"image":["//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/50px-Question_book-new.svg.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/30px-Commons-logo.svg.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/vector/images/search-ltr.png?303-4","//bits.wikimedia.org/images/wikimedia-button.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/poweredby_mediawiki_88x31.png"],"tags":[["transformers","toy_line"],["spawn","comics"],["he-man_and_the_masters_of_the_universe","2002"],["joker","comics"],["leech","masters_of_the_universe"],["flocking","texture"],["transformers","toy_line"],["teenage_mutant_ninja_turtles","action_figures"],["joker","comics"]],"members":["flocking","transformers","joker","teenage_mutant_ninja_turtles","leech","spawn"],"related":["Figurine","Collecting","Ha